Program: Discovery
Title: Keyhole Surgery
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03jrwbx
Last Broadcast Date: 06 December 1994
A special report on keyhole surgery. "This is one of the quantum leaps in medical therapy in the last century," says Professor John Wickham. "Manipulating through small holes reduces the trauma radically." Presenter Geoff Watts.